body:
Ok, I downgraded scipy based on [this](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/38854513/conda-python-import-error-image-not-found-in-jupyter-notebook-only)
```
 conda install scipy=0.17.0
```
which seems to have helped (at least in the terminal. Spyder still displays original error).
Now I get memory issues, which I think are unrelated to this original issue, so I'm going to close this issue. 

Thanks 👯‍♂️
